comments: Alan is absolutely one of the most Hilarious teachers I have taken a course with. Most of the actual subject of the lesson gets lost in his constant off topic banter, which is more often than not, more interesting than the academic subject itself. After taking multiple classes with Alan I have many water cooler conversation starters.
